  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >• <strong>Community reviews</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100810/extras/4b859d044243edaf09259855e4e71698.avif?t=1751083772\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100810/extras_big/4b859d044243edaf09259855e4e71698.avif?t=1751083772 width=800 height=228 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100810/extras/53ac97122e4e305e915002b1342b1887.avif?t=1751083772\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100810/extras_big/53ac97122e4e305e915002b1342b1887.avif?t=1751083772 width=800 height=176 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100810/extras/688b5968d1a8ae7a07b2de7cc67f15d9.avif?t=1751083772\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100810/extras_big/688b5968d1a8ae7a07b2de7cc67f15d9.avif?t=1751083772 width=800 height=204 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Unreal WuKong\" is an open-world action RPG based on the classic Chinese mythological novel, \"Journey to the West.\" You will play as the Monkey King, Sun Wukong, embarking on a perilous and wondrous adventure to save the world by vanquishing demons that have traveled from the future.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >• Open World, Free Exploration</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Developed using Unreal Engine 5, the game constructs a breathtakingly beautiful and fantastical open world with ultra-realistic graphics. A vast and detailed world awaits your exploration, filled with stunning details and hidden treasures. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100810/extras/e15b40123340a1edd492838c81c0852c.poster.avif?t=1751083772\" width=700 height=394 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100810/extras/e15b40123340a1edd492838c81c0852c.webm?t=1751083772\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100810/extras/e15b40123340a1edd492838c81c0852c.mp4?t=1751083772\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100810/extras/0e728e59233a9f4fbd937104ffe7f154.poster.avif?t=1751083772\" width=700 height=394 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100810/extras/0e728e59233a9f4fbd937104ffe7f154.webm?t=1751083772\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100810/extras/0e728e59233a9f4fbd937104ffe7f154.mp4?t=1751083772\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100810/extras/3def549197f760cdc396b50c2d0fa977.poster.avif?t=1751083772\" width=700 height=394 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100810/extras/3def549197f760cdc396b50c2d0fa977.webm?t=1751083772\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100810/extras/3def549197f760cdc396b50c2d0fa977.mp4?t=1751083772\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >• The Great Sage, Defeating Demons</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Play as Sun Wukong, the legendary Monkey King, with his invincible iron body. Face off against iconic demons from Journey to the West in intense battles as the Great Sage.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100810/extras/1c569d956455e0eb4011909cd14c72c8.poster.avif?t=1751083772\" width=700 height=394 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100810/extras/1c569d956455e0eb4011909cd14c72c8.webm?t=1751083772\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100810/extras/1c569d956455e0eb4011909cd14c72c8.mp4?t=1751083772\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100810/extras/0b39f4edf16284575493544fbd39791b.poster.avif?t=1751083772\" width=700 height=394 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100810/extras/0b39f4edf16284575493544fbd39791b.webm?t=1751083772\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100810/extras/0b39f4edf16284575493544fbd39791b.mp4?t=1751083772\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >• Magic Staff, Boundless Power</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > The Ruyi Jingu Bang can extend and contract at will, allowing for both ranged and melee combat. Sun Wukong is equipped with teleportation, invincible iron body, and 72 transformations, making him formidable against any foe.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100810/extras/ead5c565b7fad1b811b97f82e6a338a8.poster.avif?t=1751083772\" width=700 height=394 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100810/extras/ead5c565b7fad1b811b97f82e6a338a8.webm?t=1751083772\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100810/extras/ead5c565b7fad1b811b97f82e6a338a8.mp4?t=1751083772\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100810/extras/04c3c79b98adfca5897e362d08a21b6d.poster.avif?t=1751083772\" width=700 height=394 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100810/extras/04c3c79b98adfca5897e362d08a21b6d.webm?t=1751083772\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100810/extras/04c3c79b98adfca5897e362d08a21b6d.mp4?t=1751083772\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100810/extras/fa4be00c415cd327ac74f6e1d09462d7.poster.avif?t=1751083772\" width=700 height=394 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100810/extras/fa4be00c415cd327ac74f6e1d09462d7.webm?t=1751083772\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100810/extras/fa4be00c415cd327ac74f6e1d09462d7.mp4?t=1751083772\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >• Equipment System, Character Growth</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Continuously improve Sun Wukong's abilities through battles and quests, unlocking new skills and equipment. Forge a unique and unparalleled Great Sage.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100810/extras/bd65a002136b7183515b